A version of Pang written in Python using Pygame
Joseph Bleau
http://www.josephbleau.com

You must have Python 2.7 and PyGame installed if you wish to run this from source. 

You can download PyGame here: http://www.pygame.org/download.shtml

For a self-extracting / running binary of Pang, download here: http://www.josephbleau.com/pang.exe